        <abstract>
            <p>CD would have carried the public more if he had explained adaptations by multiple causes, some unknown and some well known, i.e., natural selection.</p>
            <p>Discusses Hooker’s views of extinction on St Helena.</p>
            <p>Work on antiquity of man suspended.</p> 
<p>Stopped by 11th edition of <hi rend="italic">Principles of geology</hi> [1872].</p> 
        </abstract>
